Received an updated brokerage report Monday (filing day) which moved some 1099
dividend income to the non-taxable distribution box. Jeez I am not going to
like having to file amended returns. I want to start now on 2007
income/gains/losses/deductions. This is all so non-productive for me. grrrr.
